er Drive”之间的合作项目“Racer VTuber Kotone Hanakan Collaboration: Drive around Town with KOTONE Racing”将于 3 月 20 日（星期三）至 6 月 23 日（星期三）举行（天）。</p><p> “Cheer Drive”是一项服务，驾驶员可以通过在汽车上贴上自己喜欢的品牌和内容的贴纸来支持公司和组织，并根据行驶距离获得福利作为回报。此次合作包括根据新绘制的插图制作成汽车贴纸的插图设计图案，以及KOTONE Racing标志设计图案。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000104.000075261.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cheer Drive Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2>九条林檎发行原创歌曲《Emotional night》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-1024x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-768x768.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-jpg.webp 1350w" width="1024" height="1024" /></a></p><p>索尼音乐娱乐公司运营的虚拟人才开发和管理项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/_vee_official_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VEE</a> ”的<a href="https://twitter.com/ringo_0_0_5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ringo Kujo</a>发布了原创歌曲“Emotional night”。</p><p> 《情感之夜》是由佐伯青年K作词、作曲、编曲的歌曲。此外，由晴明零执导的音乐录影带也已公开。</p><p><a href="https://kujoringo.lnk.to/Emotionalnight" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看音乐将在哪里分发。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="感人之夜 / 九条林檎 MV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RcZPN_Q8EeQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-me